      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "- The preview API `StructuredTaskScope` provides a first-class, readable abstraction for managing lifetimes of related tasks.\n- To run real samples with `StructuredTaskScope`, compile and run with `--enable-preview` on a supported JDK.\n- Example (CLI):\n  - `javac --enable-preview --release 26 Demo.java`\n  - `java --enable-preview Demo`\n- In this notebook we used a runnable simulation that captures behavior patterns (join, fail-fast, cancellation) without preview APIs.\n",
